FilterExpression        ::= Condition

Condition               ::= Predicate 
                        |   Condition ÔANDÕ Condition 
                        |   Condition ÔORÕ Condition 
                        |   ÔNOTÕ Condition 
                        |   Ô(Õ Condition Ô)Õ 
                        . 

Predicate               ::= ComparisonPredicate 
                        |   BetweenPredicate 
                        .
 
ComparisonPredicate     ::= FIELDNAME RelOp Parameter 
                        |   Parameter RelOp FIELDNAME 
                        |   FIELDNAME RelOp FIELDNAME 
                        . 

BetweenPredicate        ::= FIELDNAME ÔBETWEENÕ Range 
                        |   FIELDNAME ÔNOT BETWEENÕ Range 
                        . 

RelOp                   ::= Ô=Õ | Ô>Õ | Ô>=Õ | Ô<Õ | Ô<=Õ | Ô<>Õ | like 
                        .
 
Range                   ::= Parameter ÔANDÕ Parameter 
                        .
 
Parameter               ::= INTEGERVALUE 
                        |   CHARVALUE 
                        |   FLOATVALUE 
                        |   STRING  
                        |   ENUMERATEDVALUE 
                        |   PARAMETER 